name: to tired - the vortex e.p
description:
First self release by sound artist to tired www.myspace.com/totired
A record of re-ordered feild recordings based on stone tape theory.
Remixes of events before and after they've happend. The culmination of weeks shortened down into just over ten minuetes.
Hand made case from the vortex performance at Witton Park Blackburn.

name: brown orange blue - natto and cab
description:
Brown Orange Blue's- natto and cab is a collection of songs  ressemble part folk part electronic combination.With a mixture synth, sample wizardry this symbiotic bleand of ideas always has a joyfull aspect to it; in the quick paced 'other people and tom' and  even in serious subject matter like 'first prize'.From start to finish this record celebrates the cohesion of synthetic and organic sounds.In the space of year this band has gone from something kept in the bedroom studio to a live act that's well underway with its new album.
